<div class="text"><p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2>Undergraduate Research at Ryerson: Funding and Opportunities &nbsp;&nbsp;</h2>
<p>In order to participate in world-class research opportunities at Ryerson, undergraduate students are encouraged to approach individual <a href="/content/ryerson/cab/FacultyStaff.html#center_tabs">faculty members within the department</a> and seek out research and funding opportunites with them.<br /></p>
<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Funded opportunities include:</p>
<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - <a href="http://www.nserc-crsng.gc.ca/students-etudiants/ug-pc/usra-brpc_eng.asp" target="_blank">NSERC URSA</a></p>
<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - <a href="/research/services/funding/index.html" target="_blank">RYERSON URO</a><br /></p>
<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - <a href="/research/services/funding/index.html" target="_blank">Work Study Research assistantships</a><br /></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
